{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3355ba327f","title":"在延安中央党校的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c65ae47af9","index":0,"year":1944,"month":11,"day":null,"articleId":"3355ba327f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui2","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1943-1949卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui2a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c7bf731cc1","type":"title","text":"在延安中央党校的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"3355ba327f"},{"id":"d733ae0c97","type":"paragraph","text":"有的同志脑袋像个西瓜一样，西瓜表面是绿的，很纯净没有什么，但是切开一看，都是旁的颜色，红瓤黑籽，啥都有。有人表面看挺好，脑袋里装着自私自利，有封建迷信......，这些复杂的观念是我们的包袱，就是敌人。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"3355ba327f"}],"page":{"id":"78b87edce1","publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"3355ba327f","start":53,"end":53}}}},"__N_SSG":true}